snippet.title: GunboundM Introduction
snippet.description:
GunboundM introduction
We made the Gunbound PC version a long time ago.
We try to make the next generation of Gunbound.

Players have to judge the wind and aim and fire quickly.
In the new Gunbound, various game situations and strategies continue.
New game elements such as clouds and totems are also added.
Let's Play together! (Android, iOS)

-Download-
GooglePlay: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.DargomStudio.GunboundM.Global
APPLE iOS: https://itunes.apple.com/app/id1221174690

-Community-
http://cafe.naver.com/gunboundm (한글)
https://www.plug.game/gunboundm-en (English)
